==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Postglacial
<hw>Post*gla"cial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Geol.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>Formed or occurring after the last glacial epoch of
the Pleistocene period, or at a locality within the area of Pleistocene
glaciation after the final disappearance of the glacier from the
locality.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>Of, pertaining to, or designating, an
epoch after the last Glacial and before the Terrace epoch.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Postglenoid</ent>⟦br⟧
